ing predictable. Available in wine and cocktail inspired palettes to camouflage spills. Our double-sided table linens have a distinct design on the front and back where the pattern shifts in scale and the colors vibrate in surprising combinations on each side. The dinner napkins are printed on 100% cotton shantung with a light woven texture and a luxurious touch. \\u003c\\/span\\u003e\\u003c\\/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cbr\\u003e\\u003cbr\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003e\\u003cmeta charset=\\\"utf-8\\\"\\u003e\\u003cspan\\u003eDinner napkins are sold as a set of 4. \\u003cem\\u003e\\n\\u003c\\/em\\u003e\\u003c\\/span\\u003e\\u003c\\/p\\u003e\\u003cbr\\u003e\\nMK Finds items are not eligible for discounts. \",\"published_at\":\"2026-03-24T10:21:36-04:00\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-17T13:19:06-04:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-04-17T09:35:14-04:00\",\"vendor\":\"Tortuga Forma\",\"product_type\":\"Table Linens\",\"tags\":[\"badge-MK Finds\",\"badge-Tortuga Forma\",\"Shopify Collective\",\"Tortuga Forma\"],\"variants\":[{\"id\":42571212750910,\"title\":\"Grid Martini\",\"option1\":\"Grid Martini\",\"option2\":null,\"option3\":null,\"sku\":\"TL-DGRID-TINI\",\"requires_shipping\":true,\"taxable\":true,\"featured_image\":{\"id\":35776435945534,\"product_id\":8039266385982,\"position\":1,\"created_at\":\"2026-03-24T16:42:56-04:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-24T16:42:58-04:00\",\"alt\":null,\"width\":1277,\"height\":1641,\"src\":\"https:\\/\\/cdn.shopify.com\\/s\\/files\\/1\\/2304\\/7781\\/files\\/Tortuga_Forma_reversible_grid_cloth_napkins_in_olive.png?v=1774384978\",\"variant_ids\":[42571212750910]},\"available\":true,\"price\":\"88.00\",\"grams\":227,\"compare_at_price\":null,\"position\":1,\"product_id\":8039266385982,\"created_at\":\"2026-03-17T13:19:06-04:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-04-17T09:35:14-04:00\"},{\"id\":42571212783678,\"title\":\"Grid Vino\",\"option1\":\"Grid Vino\",\"option2\":null,\"option3\":null,\"sku\":\"TL-DGRID-VIN\",\"requires_shipping\":true,\"taxable\":true,\"featured_im